{"tid":1217623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中》香港年輕人送雨傘、頭盔 美國CBS記者PO影片道謝","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:43:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b138fe85ef3776a72e0f17547c0e90608c4889","tid":1217623,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"許多香港民眾上街參加「反送中運動」，警方昨（12）日使用各式武器進行驅離、清場，朝民眾投擲超過150枚催淚彈，不少記者也受到波及，一名美國CBS電視台記者今天PO出了一段影片，要感謝在反送中行動中給他雨傘和頭盔的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\nCBS電視台駐亞洲記者英若明（Ramy Inocencio）在Twitter上PO出了自己在佔領現場的情況，當時他正講解民眾和警方對峙的狀況，幾位示威的年輕人直接將雨傘及頭盔送給了深入前線的他，讓他相當感激地直呼：謝謝，唔該唔該。<br />\n<br />\n英若明表示拍攝現場當時遭到警方投擲信號彈，雨傘和頭盔保護了毫無防備的他，即使他有可能一輩子都不會知道這些年輕人是誰，但他只想透過這個影片道謝，也對這些年輕人貼心、友善的舉動相當感動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2821659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821659&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c73515aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821659&h=1eaed71e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2821659</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/RamyInocencio/status/1138978532640485377?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1138978532640485377&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FRamyInocencio%2Fstatus%2F1138978532640485377%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1138978532640485377%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnews.ltn.com.tw%252Fnews%252Fworld%252Fbreakingnews%252F2821659&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=b098d797\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/RamyInocencio/status/1138978532640485377?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1138978532640485377&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821659</a>"},{"pid":"7e4aef8a2e65da05cf0de25ed3377410a4884de8","tid":1217623,"uid":140802,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"好多人都有讚香港人<br />\n大家愈來愈得到國際支持<br />\n繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726a83861ac6c63565da3d6793277bdfffd8ef5a","tid":1217623,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce76a4abb0b5239bd365f2d8926908d8d12f948","tid":1217623,"uid":33668,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"警察射記者<br />\n暴徒救記者<br />\nThis is Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n一哥英文翻譯版<br />\nEreeeerer police shoot errr press<br />\nErr Violent people safe press<br />\n<br />\n真心"}]}